text: The Zobel Lady Junior Archers may refer to the women's football team of the De La Salle Santiago Zobel School which competes in the PFF Women's League, the top-flight women's football league in the Philippines. De La Salle Zobel along with Tuloy F.C. debuted in the 2018 season of the league. Their first league match was on August 25, 2018 where they were routed by OutKast 2–10. ==See also== *Zobel Junior Archers – for the athletic program of De La Salle Santiago Zobel School in general. ==References== Category:University Athletic Association of the Philippines football teams Category:Women's football clubs in the Philippines Category:PFF Women's League clubs
